lead_paragraph: Lee Stempniak scored his first goal as a Bruin in overtime and Boston beat Florida 5-4 on Monday night while Panthers forward Jaromir Jagr moved into third on the NHL career points list.

headline.print_headline: Stempniak Scores in OT, Bruins Beat Panthers 5-4
